Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.symptomaticapp.User
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Caregiver

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    A user is a user of the application who will have an account, which has contact information including an email, a phone number, and a username. Furthermore, it will have a list of problems associated with the account
